Biomarkers of immune function (systemic low-level inflammation), which also are myokines, will be assessed using a MILLIPLEX MAP Human Cytokine/Chemokine Magnetic Bead Panel Immunology Multiplex Assay read with a Luminex xMAP® platform (Merck Millipore, Darmstadt, Germany) in a magnetic bead format for the determination (pg.ml
					
						−1
					) of: IL-1β, IL-6, IL-10, IL-15, INF-γ, fibroblast growth factor 2 (FGF2), CX3CL1 (fractalkine), CCL2 (monocyte chemotactic protein-1: MCP-1), TNF-α, vascular endothelial derived growth factor (VEGF) and brain-derived neurotrophic factor (BDNF). Precision data given by the manufacturer estimate accuracy as 87 to 107%. Intra-assay and inter-assay CVs are given as 2 to 13% and 5 to 19%, respectively.
